data.name: lblDeveloperDefinition.Text
data.value: Student at the Faculty of Computers and Artificial Intelligence. The author of the book "The Engineer in Python", dedicated to simplifying programming concepts for beginners. This application is my first app i developed using C#.NET Framework(Windows Form) I know this technology is somewhat outdated, but it was part of my foundational journey with Mr. Abu-Hadhoud. I will transition to modern technologies soon, Insha'Allah. And it is currently not connected to a database, because I'm still on my way to be a software engineer. but i will integrate it with database soon, Insha'Allah. Let me know if you have any suggestions!
